<i>noun</i>: 후회 [후ː회/후ː훼], 회한 [회ː한/훼ː한], 참회 [참회/참훼], 자책감 [자책깜], 반성 [반ː성] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>후회 [후ː회/후ː훼]</dt><br>
<dd>regret; remorse; repentance</dd><br>
<dd>이전에 자신이 한 일이 잘못임을 깨닫고 스스로 자신의 잘못을 꾸짖음.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of realizing that what one did was wrong and reprimanding oneself for having done it.</dd><br>
<dt>회한 [회ː한/훼ː한]</dt><br>
<dd>regret; remorse; contrition</dd><br>
<dd>잘못 등을 뉘우치고 한숨을 쉬며 탄식함.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of letting out a sigh and grieving while regretting one's wrongdoings.</dd><br>
<dt>참회 [참회/참훼]</dt><br>
<dd>repentance; remorse; self-reproach</dd><br>
<dd>잘못을 깨닫고 부끄럽게 생각하여 뉘우침.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of realizing one's shameful wrongdoings and regretting them.</dd><br>
<dt>자책감 [자책깜]</dt><br>
<dd>guilty conscience; remorse; pangs of conscience</dd><br>
<dd>스스로 잘못했다고 생각하여 자신을 꾸짖고 나무라는 마음.</dd><br>
<dd>A state of mind that scolds and rebukes oneself for one's own wrongdoing.</dd><br>
<dt>반성 [반ː성]</dt><br>
<dd>1. introspection; self-contemplation</dd><br>
<dd>자신의 말이나 행동을 되돌아보면서 잘못을 살피거나 그것을 깨닫고 뉘우침.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of looking back on one's words or conduct and reflecting on or repenting one's mistake.</dd><br>
<dd>2. remorse</dd><br>
<dd>자신의 잘못을 깨닫고 뉘우침.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of realizing and repenting one's mistake.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>